entation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/travel.html\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports.html\">Canadian passports and other travel documents</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwstitle section\">\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">\nContact the Passport Program</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>Tell us what you’re asking about to find out how you can reach us.</p>\n<div data-wb-jsonmanager='{\n\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/ircc/documents/json/data-passport-ptime.json\",\n\t\t\"name\": \"ptime\"\n\t}' id=\"jsonmanagerpassportprocessingtime\"></div>\n<div class=\"wb-frmvld\" id=\"fftool\">\n<form method=\"get\">\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow hidden gc-font-2019\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\n \t\t\t\"noForm\": true,\n\t\t\t\"renderas\":\"radio\",\n\"gcChckbxrdio\":true,\n            \"base\": { \"live\": true, \"renderas\":\"radio\",\"gcChckbxrdio\":true },\n            \"hideelm\": \".pe, #korahCcrChatContainer\",\n            \"unhideelm\": \"#fftool, #ff-details-1, #ff-details-2\",\n            \"default\": [{\"action\": \"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\":\".result1, .result2, .result3, .2h, .3h, #korahCcrChatContainer, .alert-wildfire\"} ]\n\t\t\t}'>\n<p><strong>I have a question about:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Passports\n          <div class=\"wb-fieldflow-sub\">\n<p>Where are you?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result1,#korahCcrChatContainer,.alert-wildfire\"}'>Canada </li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result2\"}'>United States </li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".result3\"}'>Outside Canada and the US</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".2h\"}'>Certificates of identity or refugee travel documents</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"toggle\", \"toggle\": \".3h\"}'>Media inquiries</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 alert-wildfire pe\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 result1 result2 result3 pe\">\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"contact-us-passport/passport-contact-questions-en\"></span>\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-sm\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"\" src=\"/content/dam/ircc/migration/ircc/english/helpcentre/images/Icon.png\"/> Top questions about passports</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/help-centre/apply.html#renew\">When should I renew my passport</a>?</li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/renew-adult-passport/renew-who.html\">Can I renew my passport instead of applying for a new one</a>?</li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/fees/passport-travel-document-refunds.html\">Do I get a refund if my application wasn’t processed within the service standards</a>?</li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/dual-canadian-citizens-visit-canada.html\">I’m a dual citizen. Do I need my Canadian passport to return to Canada</a>?</li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/help-centre/apply.html#missing-documents\">I got my new passport, but my supporting documents are missing. What should I do</a>?</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=140&amp;top=18\">How do I open your application forms</a>?</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/help-centre.html\">See all questions in the Help Centre</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"well\" id=\"apply\">\n<h2 class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-sm\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-user-check\"></span> Get your passport application status instantly</h2>\n<p>Avoid waiting on the phone and check your application status online.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/check-passport-travel-document-application.html\">Check your passport application status</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 result1 pe\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2>Contact us about your passport in Canada</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-post-strike-en\" id=\"long\"></span>\n<!-- <div class=\"ajax\"> <span data-incl-name=\"passport-post-strike-en\" id=\"long\"></span>\n  <div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n    <details>\n  <summary>\n    <h2 class=\"h4\">Passport services are available during the Canada Post labour disruption</h2>\n  </summary>\n  <p>We’re processing passport applications as usual. However, you <strong>may</strong> experience some delays receiving your passport by mail following recent Canada Post labour disruptions.</p>\n  <p><a href=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/canada-post-2025.html\">Learn how we’re delivering passports during the labour disruption</a>.</p>\n</details>\n  </div>\n</div>-->\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n<h2 class=\"h4\">Possible passport delivery delays</h2>\n<p>We’re processing passport applications as usual. However, you <strong>may</strong> experience some delays receiving your passport by mail following recent Canada Post labour disruptions.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>You can contact us online, by phone, by visiting our office or by mail.</p>\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-laptop fa-2x mrgn-rght-sm\"></span> Online</h3>\n<p>You can reach us several ways depending on what you want to contact us about.</p>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign\"></span> <a href=\"https://contact-esdc-edsc.service.canada.ca/en/contact/index.html?id=passport_pptg\">Ask us a question</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up\"></span> <a href=\"https://contact-esdc-edsc.service.canada.ca/en/contact/index.html?id=passport_ppty\">Give us a compliment</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down\"></span> <a href=\"https://contact-esdc-edsc.service.canada.ca/en/contact/index.html?id=passport_pptc\">Submit a complaint</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-comment\"></span> <a href=\"https://contact-esdc-edsc.service.canada.ca/en/contact/index.html?id=passport_ppti\">Give us feedback on our forms</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-phone-alt fa-2x\"></span>  Call us</h3>\n<p>We answer calls Monday to Friday, from 8:30 am to 5 pm, your local time (9:00 am to 5:30 pm in Newfoundland). We do <strong>not</strong> answer calls on <a aria-controls=\"passport-office-holidays\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#passport-office-holidays\" role=\"button\">statutory holidays</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"row mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<p class=\"text-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-phone fa-2x\"></span></p>\n<h3 class=\"text-center\">Call our toll-free or direct number</h3>\n<p>You can reach us at either of the numbers below.</p>\n<p class=\"text-center\">Toll-free number:<br/><strong class=\"nowrap\">1‑800‑567‑6868</strong></p>\n<p class=\"text-center\">Direct number:<br/><strong class=\"nowrap\">1‑819‑997‑8338</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<p class=\"text-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-tty fa-2x\"></span></p>\n<h3 class=\"text-center\">Use our TTY service</h3>\n<p>If you’re hearing impaired or have a speech impediment, you can use our TTY service.</p>\n<p class=\"text-center nowrap\"><strong>1‑866‑255‑7655</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Data from ESDC Starts-->\n<details class=\"hidden\" id=\"ff-details-1\">\n<summary><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-time\"></span> Average wait times <span class=\"label label-info\">Last updated: <span data-json-replacewith=\"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/meta/passportUpdateDate\"></span></span></summary>\n<p>Find out the average time it took us to answer calls during the week.</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<table class=\"table table-responsive\" data-wb-json='{ \"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/daily\", \"type\": \"addclass\" }'>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"col-md-1\" scope=\"col\">Day</th>\n<th class=\"col-md-2\" scope=\"col\">Average Wait Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody data-wb-json='{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/daily\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"nocache\":\"nocache\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"source\": \"#tbl2\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"tobeclone\": \"tr\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"mapping\": [\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td\", \"value\": \"/text\"},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td:nth-child(2)\", \"value\": \"/passport\"}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t]\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}'>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<template id=\"tbl2\">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</template>\n<details>\n<summary>Weekly average wait times</summary>\n<div class=\"table-responsive mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<table class=\"table table-responsive\" data-wb-json='{ \"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/weekly\", \"type\": \"addclass\" }'>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"col-md-1\" scope=\"col\">Week</th>\n<th class=\"col-md-2\" scope=\"col\">Average Wait Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody data-wb-json='{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/weekly\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"nocache\":\"nocache\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"source\": \"#tbl3\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"tobeclone\": \"tr\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"mapping\": [\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td\", \"value\": \"/text\"},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td:nth-child(2)\", \"value\": \"/passport\"}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t]\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}'>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<template id=\"tbl3\">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</template>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Monthly average wait times</summary>\n<div class=\"table-responsive mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<table class=\"table\" data-wb-json='{ \"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/monthly\", \"type\": \"addclass\"}'>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"col-md-1\" scope=\"col\">Month</th>\n<th class=\"col-md-2\" scope=\"col\">Average Wait Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody data-wb-json='{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/monthly\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"nocache\":\"nocache\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"source\": \"#tbl4\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"tobeclone\": \"tr\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"mapping\": [\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td\", \"value\": \"/text\"},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td:nth-child(2)\", \"value\": \"/passport\"}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t]\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}'>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<template id=\"tbl4\">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</template>\n</details>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-building fa-2x\"></span>  Find an office</h3>\n<p>You can visit us at a Service Canada Centre or passport office near you.</p>\n<p>If you haven’t booked an appointment, you can check the walk-in wait time before you go.</p>\n<p class=\"text-center\"><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/passport/map/map.asp\"><strong>Find a service location</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<details>\n<summary>Contact us by mail</summary>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<h3>Mailing address (non-courier)</h3>\n<p>Passport Program<br/>\n\t\t\tGatineau QC  K1A 0G3<br/>\n\t\t\tCanada</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<h3>Courier address</h3>\n<p>Passport Program<br/>\n\t\t\t22 de Varennes Street<br/>\n\t\t\tGatineau QC  J8T 8R1<br/>\n\t\t\tCanada</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</details>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-office-holidays-en\"></span>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"passport-office-holidays\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title\">Office closures for statutory holidays</h2>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>Passport offices and Service Canada Centres will be closed on these dates in <strong>2026</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>January 1</li>\n<li>April 3 and 6</li>\n<li>May 18</li>\n<li>June 24 (Quebec only)</li>\n<li>July 1</li>\n<li>August 3 (except Quebec)</li>\n<li>September 7</li>\n<li>September 30</li>\n<li>October 12</li>\n<li>November 11</li>\n<li>December 25 and 28</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 result2 pe\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2>Contact us about your passport from the US</h2>\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-laptop fa-2x mrgn-rght-sm\"></span> Online</h3>\n<p>You can reach us several ways depending on what you want to contact us about.</p>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/general.aspx\">Ask us a question through our\n                            web form</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/compliments.aspx?GoCTemplateCulture=en-CA\">Give\n                            us a compliment</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/plainte-complaint.aspx?GoCTemplateCulture=en-CA\">Submit\n                            a complaint</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"well eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-comment\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/interform.aspx\">Give us feedback on our\n                            forms</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-phone-alt fa-2x\"></span>  Call us</h3>\n<p>We answer calls Monday to Friday, from 8:30 am to 5 pm, your local time. We do <strong>not</strong> answer\n            calls on <a aria-controls=\"passport-office-holidays\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#passport-office-holidays\">statutory holidays</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"row mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<p class=\"text-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-phone fa-2x\"></span></p>\n<h3 class=\"text-center\">Call our toll-free or direct number</h3>\n<p>You can reach us at either of the numbers below.</p>\n<p class=\"text-center\">Toll-free number:<br/><strong class=\"nowrap\">1‑800‑567‑6868</strong>\n</p>\n<p class=\"text-center\">Direct number:<br/><strong class=\"nowrap\">1‑819‑997‑8338</strong>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<p class=\"text-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-tty fa-2x\"></span></p>\n<h3 class=\"text-center\">Use our TTY service</h3>\n<p>If you’re hearing impaired or have a speech impediment, you can use our TTY service.</p>\n<p class=\"text-center nowrap\"><strong>1‑866‑255‑7655</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-wb-jsonmanager='{\n            \"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/services/passport/call-times-temps-appels.json\",\n            \"name\": \"call-time\"}' id=\"jsonmanagercalltimes2\">\n</div>\n<details class=\"hidden\" id=\"ff-details-2\">\n<summary><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-time\"></span> Average wait times <span class=\"label label-info\">Last updated: <span data-json-replacewith=\"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/meta/passportUpdateDate\"></span></span></summary>\n<p>Find out the average time it took us to answer calls during the week.</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<table class=\"table table-responsive\" data-wb-json='{ \"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/daily\", \"type\": \"addclass\" }'>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"col-md-1\" scope=\"col\">Day</th>\n<th class=\"col-md-2\" scope=\"col\">Average Wait Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody data-wb-json='{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/daily\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"nocache\":\"nocache\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"source\": \"#tbl22\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"tobeclone\": \"tr\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"mapping\": [\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td\", \"value\": \"/text\"},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td:nth-child(2)\", \"value\": \"/passport\"}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t]\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}'>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<template id=\"tbl22\">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</template>\n<details>\n<summary>Weekly average wait times</summary>\n<div class=\"table-responsive mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<table class=\"table table-responsive\" data-wb-json='{ \"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/weekly\", \"type\": \"addclass\" }'>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"col-md-1\" scope=\"col\">Week</th>\n<th class=\"col-md-2\" scope=\"col\">Average Wait Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody data-wb-json='{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/weekly\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"nocache\":\"nocache\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"source\": \"#tbl33\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"tobeclone\": \"tr\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"mapping\": [\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td\", \"value\": \"/text\"},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td:nth-child(2)\", \"value\": \"/passport\"}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t]\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}'>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<template id=\"tbl33\">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</template>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Monthly average wait times</summary>\n<div class=\"table-responsive mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<table class=\"table\" data-wb-json='{ \"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/monthly\", \"type\": \"addclass\"}'>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"col-md-1\" scope=\"col\">Month</th>\n<th class=\"col-md-2\" scope=\"col\">Average Wait Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody data-wb-json='{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/esdc-edsc/documents/corporate/contact/ei-wait-times-en.json#/monthly\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"nocache\":\"nocache\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"source\": \"#tbl44\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"tobeclone\": \"tr\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"mapping\": [\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td\", \"value\": \"/text\"},\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{ \"selector\": \"td:nth-child(2)\", \"value\": \"/passport\"}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t]\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}'>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<template id=\"tbl44\">\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n<td class=\"nowrap\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</template>\n</details>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-building fa-2x\"></span>  Find an office\n        </h3>\n<p>You can visit us at a Service Canada Centre or passport office near you.</p>\n<p>If you haven’t booked an appointment, you can check the walk-in wait time before you go.</p>\n<p class=\"text-center\"><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/passport/map/map.asp\"><strong>Find a service\n                    location</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 result3 pe\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2>Contact us about your passport from abroad</h2>\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-laptop fa-2x mrgn-rght-sm\"></span> Online</h3>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/general.aspx\">Ask us a question through our web form</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/compliments.aspx?GoCTemplateCulture=en-CA\">Give us a compliment</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/plainte-complaint.aspx?GoCTemplateCulture=en-CA\">Submit a complaint</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body eqht-trgt\">\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-comment\"></span> <a href=\"https://srv144.services.gc.ca/cgi-bin/ppt/interform.aspx\">Give us feedback on our forms</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-md\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-user fa-2x mrgn-rght-sm\"></span> In person</h3>\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-sm\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-building mrgn-rght-sm\"></span>Find the nearest office</h3>\n<p>You should <a href=\"http://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates\">contact the nearest Government of Canada office abroad</a>.</p>\n<p>Call or email them <strong>before</strong> you visit them.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n<p>Find out <a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/assistance\">how to get help in  case of emergency when you’re in a foreign country</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 2h pe\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2>Contact us about your refugee travel document or certificate of identity</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"traveldocs-contact-en\"></span>\n<p>To check the status of your application, you have to contact us. <strong>You need to be in Canada</strong> to\n        do so.</p>\n<div class=\"cnjnctn-type-or cnjnctn-sm\">\n<section class=\"cnjnctn-col\">\n<h3><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-laptop fa-2x mrgn-rght-sm\"></span> Submit a web\n                form<span class=\"wb-inv\">: Option 1 of 2</span></h3>\n<p>You can <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc/web-form.html\">contact\n                    us using our web form</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"cnjnctn-col\">\n<h3><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-phone-alt fa-2x\"></span>  Call us<span class=\"wb-inv\">: Option 2 of 2</span></h3>\n<p>You can use our automated telephone service to check the status of your application 24 hours a day, 7\n                days a week.</p>\n<p>We also answer calls Monday to Friday, 8 a.m. to 4 p.m. (your local time), except for statutory\n                holidays.</p>\n<h4>Call our toll-free number</h4>\n<p><strong>1-888-242-2100</strong></p>\n<h4>Teletypewriter (TTY) service</h4>\n<p>Call us via the Bell Relay Service <strong>if you are hearing impaired or if you have a speech\n                    impediment</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Voice to TTY:</strong> 1-800-855-0511</li>\n<li><strong>TTY to Voice:</strong> 711</li>\n<li><strong>TTY to TTY:</strong> 1-800-855-1155</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 3h pe\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2>Contact us about a passport media inquiry</h2>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h3 class=\"panel-title\">For questions about passport policies</h3>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><strong><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-phone-alt\"></span> Phone</strong></p>\n<p>Contact our Media Relations team at <strong class=\"nowrap\">1-613-952-1650</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-send\"></span> Email</strong></p>\n<p>Email our Media Relations team at <a href=\"mailto:media@cic.gc.ca\">media@cic.gc.ca</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h3 class=\"panel-title\">For questions about passport services</h3>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><strong><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-phone-alt\"></span> Phone</strong></p>\n<p>Contact Service Canada at <strong class=\"nowrap\">1-819-994-5559</strong>.</p>\n<p><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chart-bar fa-2x\"></span> You can <a href=\"/en/employment-social-development/programs/passport/statistics.html\">get Passport Program statistics</a> online. <span class=\"label label-info\">Updated weekly</span></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsmediaplayer\">\n<div id=\"ccr-reference\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-12-19\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Canadian passports and other travel documents</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/help-centre.html\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/contact-pa